        "rendered": "Spinner"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "<p><code>Spinner</code> is a component used to notify users that their action is being processed.</p>\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">import { Spinner } from '@wordpress/components';\n\nfunction Example() {\n    return &lt;Spinner /&gt;;\n}\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Best practices</h2>\n<p>The spinner component should:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Signal to users that the processing of their request is underway and will soon complete.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out the <a href=\"https://wordpress.github.io/gutenberg/?path=/docs/components-spinner--docs\">Storybook page</a> for a visual exploration of this component.</p>\n",
